sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (Portal/App)
    participant API as Laravel API
    participant EL as Event Log
    participant Handler as Event Handler
    participant State as Materialized State

    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/additions (with idempotency_key)
    API->>API: Validate request
    API->>EL: EventLogger::log() → INSERT into events table
    Note over EL: Immutable. Never UPDATE or DELETE.
    EL-->>Handler: Event dispatched (via EventProcessor)
    Handler->>State: Update materialized state (additions, SO2 totals, etc.)
    Note over Handler,State: Per-event handlers partially wired. Full dispatch planned.
    API-->>Client: 201 Created (event_id)

    Note over Client,State: Offline flow (Cellar/POS apps — future phases)

    Client->>Client: Write to local SQLite
    Client->>Client: Queue event in local outbox
    Note over Client: App works normally offline
    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/events/sync (batch)
    API->>API: Check idempotency_key (skip duplicates)
    API->>EL: INSERT new events
    EL-->>Handler: Process each event
    API-->>Client: 200 OK (synced event IDs)
    Client->>Client: Mark events as synced
    Client->>API: GET /api/v1/sync/pull (latest state)
    API-->>Client: Updated materialized state
